1. *Ovakvo* vreme nije za izlazak. (This kind of weather is not suitable for going out.)
2. Nisam video *ovakvu* frizuru ranije. (I haven't seen this kind of hairstyle before.)
3. *Ovakvog* čoveka ne možeš lako prevariti. (You can't easily fool a person like this.)
4. Koliko košta *ovakva* torba? (How much does a bag like this cost?)
5. Ne volim *ovakve* situacije. (I don't like situations like this.)
6. *Ovakvim* alatom možeš da popraviš to. (You can fix that with this kind of tool.)
7. *Ovakvih* problema smo se ranije već suočili. (We've faced problems like this before.)
8. Nismo navikli na *ovakve* gužve. (We're not used to crowds like this.)
9. Ukoliko imaš *ovakvu* knjigu, pozajmi mi je. (If you have a book like this, lend it to me.)
10. *Ovakvoj* hrani se ne mogu odoleti. (I can't resist this kind of food.)